  See Stýphane Dion on MOD!!! Tuesday, October 07, 2008 Leader of the Opposition, Stéphane Dion of the Liberal Party, is taking time out from his kinda-totally-busy campaign schedule to stop by MuchOnDemand , this Wednesday, October 8, and we want you to be here! Stéphane will join our very own Hannah Simone and Devon Soltendieck to chat, discuss platforms and talk politics on the special episode of MOD. You can be a part of the audience by emailing or be at Much by 3PM on Wednesday. The show tapes from 4-5PM ET, and will go to air at 5PM! Get your questions ready because Stéphane will be answering them. And if you can't make it down, send us your question, by email or webcam, to . (Photo courtesy of Liberal.ca ) Related Stories Wednesday, September 10, 2008 Thursday, July 31, 2008 Friday, May 16, 2008 Tuesday, October 07, 2008 Tuesday, October 07, 2008 Tuesday, October 07, 2008 Tuesday, October 07, 2008 Tuesday, October 07, 2008 Tuesday, October 07, 2008 Tuesday, October 07, 2008 Monday, October 06, 2008 Monday, October 06, 2008 Monday, October 06, 2008 | | | | | 